

=Bio=

Koutsouti Effrosyni (Greece). Anthropologist, vice-president of the Documentation and Research Center of Ikaria and president of the Women's Cooperative of Katafygi. She is active in the local movement against industrial reneawable energy (Save Pramnos), which is allied with Movement 18 Against the Selling-Out of Natural Resources and the Destruction of the Natural and Cultural Capital of Greece. 


